s if from nowhere\u2014muttering incantations, placing curses, and giving people terrifying visions."},{"version":"moon","text":"Mismagius have been known to cast spells to make people fall in love, so some people search for this Pok\u00e9mon as if their life depended on it."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Feared for its wrath and the curses it spreads, this Pok\u00e9mon will also, on a whim, cast spells that help people."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Its muttered curses can cause awful headaches or terrifying visions that torment others."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"The incantations Mismagius chants can ward against misfortune, so a custom exists of inviting it into one's home. Incur the Pok\u00e9mon's displeasure, however, and disaster will surely ensue."}],"evo":{"name":"misdreavus","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"mismagius","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"use-item","item":"dusk-stone","held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/429.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/429.png","capture":45,"happiness":35,"growth":"fast","gender":4,"hatch":25,"ev":{"special_attack":1,"special_defense":1},"forms":[]}